                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='9427' id='12' type-v2='text' w='99292' x='354' y='89970'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Median income and bachelor’s degree attainment show a positive relationship, with higher-income counties tending to have higher education levels. Unemployment shows a slight inverse relationship, decreasing as income rises. Ross and Scioto counties stand out as stronger performers across multiple metrics, which aligns with their larger population centers in the region.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
